h2 Agregá tu cancha

p Si tenés o conoces un complejo que no está en nuestra base de datos, te damos la posibilidad de sumarlo a nuestro sitio.
p Te pedimos que ingreses a continuación los datos correspondientes al complejo. Los campos con marcados con (*) son obligatorios.
	form.form-horizontal
		.form-group
			label.control-label.col-sm-3(for='description') Ingresá el nombre del complejo (*)
			.col-sm-6
				input#description.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Algún nombre', ng-model='description')
		.form-group
			label.control-label.col-sm-3(for='info') Escribí una breve descripción
			.col-sm-6
				input#info.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Alguna descripción', ng-model='info')
		.form-group.search-group
			label.control-label.col-sm-3(for='address') Buscá la ubicación en el mapa (*)
			.col-sm-6
				.input-group
					input#address.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Alguna dirección', ng-model='address', ng-enter='addressSearch()')
					span.input-group-btn
						button.btn.btn-primary(type='button', ng-class='{ disabled: loadingAddress }', ng-click='addressSearch()') {{loadingAddress ? 'Buscando ...' : 'Buscar'}}
				ol(ng-show='addressResults.length > 0')
					li(ng-repeat='result in addressResults') 
						a(href='', ng-click='setAddress(result)') {{result.address}}
				#map-add.map-canvas
		.form-group
			label.control-label.col-sm-3(for='phone') Indicanos algún teléfono
			.col-sm-6
				input#phone.form-control(type='tel', placeholder='Algún teléfono', ng-model='phone')        
		.form-group.courts-list
			label.control-label.col-sm-3(for='') Canchas del complejo
			.col-sm-6
				label.control-label.col-sm-3(for='sport') Deporte
				.col-sm-9
					select#sport.form-control(ng-model='currentCourt.sport' ng-options='t.name for t in sports')
						option(value='') [Seleccione]
			.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3(ng-show='currentCourt.sport.allowPlayers')
				label.control-label.col-sm-3(for='players') Jugadores
				.col-sm-9
					input#players.form-control(type='number', placeholder='Alguna cantidad', ng-model='currentCourt.players' ng-init='null')  
			.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3
				label.control-label.col-sm-3(for='surface') Superficie
				.col-sm-9
					select#surface.form-control(ng-disabled='currentCourt.sport == null', ng-model='currentCourt.surface', ng-options='s for s in currentCourt.sport.surfaces')
						option(value='') [Seleccione]
			.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3
				label.control-label.col-sm-3 ¿Es techada?
				.col-sm-9
					.checkbox
						label
							input#isIndoor(type='checkbox', ng-disabled='currentCourt.sport == null', ng-model='currentCourt.isIndoor', ng-init='false')
			.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3
				a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xs.pull-right(ng-click='addCourt(currentCourt)') Agregar cancha
			.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3.courts-current-list(ng-show='courts.length > 0')
				label.control-label.col-sm-3 Listado
				ul.col-sm-9
					li(ng-repeat='group in groupedCourts') 
						strong {{group.key}}
						ul
							li.court-current-list-detail(ng-repeat='court in group')
								a.pull-right.btn.btn-primary.btn-xs.btn-court-action(ng-click='addCourt(court[0])' href='') +
								a.pull-right.btn.btn-primary.btn-xs.btn-court-action(ng-click='removeCourt(court[0])' href='') -
								span {{court.length}} cancha{{court.length > 1 ? 's' : null}} de {{court.key.surface}}{{court.key.isIndoor ? ', techada' + (court.length > 1 ? 's' : '') : null}}{{court.key.players ? ', para ' + court.key.players + ' jugadores' : null}}&nbsp;
		.form-group
			label.control-label.col-sm-3(for='tags') Detallá los servicios que ofrece (bar, vestuarios, estacionamiento, etc.)
			.col-sm-6
				.form-control.tag-search(ng-class='{ focused: focused, "has-no-tags": tags.length == 0 }', ng-focus-input='', data-hint='Para agregar más de un servicio, escribí lo que desees y presioná la tecla ↲' class='hint--right hint--info hint--rounded')
					span.label.label-primary(ng-repeat='tag in tags') {{tag}}
						button.close(type='button', ng-click='removeTag(tag)') &times;
					input#tags(type='text', maxlength='18', placeholder='{{tags.length == 0 ? "Algún servicio" : null}}' ng-model='currentTag' ng-class='{ "text-danger": validateTag(currentTag) }' ng-enter='addTag(currentTag)' ng-focus='focused = true', ng-blur='focused = false')
		.form-group
			.col-sm-offset-3.col-sm-6
				button.btn.btn-primary(type='submit', ng-click='save()') ¡Agregar complejo!